    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は撮影よろしくな、三人とも\nただ、内容について一つ、変更があるそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ let's do the shooting well‚ all three of us.\nHowever‚ there's one change in the content.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1,
      "endTime": 8.713903590600001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "変更……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A change…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9333333333,
      "endTime": 10.9116099914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "実は、瑠依のキスシーンなんだけど……\nカットになったらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ it's about Rui's kissing scene…\nIt seems it got cut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1,
      "endTime": 16.435932933700002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "え！　……そう、ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!… Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6333333333,
      "endTime": 20.8819047769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも、相手役の俳優さんの都合が悪くなって\n急遽台本を変えることになったそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems that the actor who was supposed to be the partner had some issues‚\nso they had to change the script suddenly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0666666667,
      "endTime": 26.7910738456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことであれば、分かりました\n修正台本、読み込んでおきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that's the case‚ I understand.\nI'll take a look at the revised script…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9666666667,
      "endTime": 32.123174573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……優？\nどうしたの？　さっきから凄いニコニコしてるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yu-chan?\nWhat's wrong? You've been smiling so much since earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2666666667,
      "endTime": 38.3634367061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　なんでもないです～\nせっかく練習したのに、残念やな～キスシーン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~? It's nothing~\nIt's a shame‚ we practiced so hard‚ but the kissing scene got cut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5666666667,
      "endTime": 46.1960785296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "（……優ちゃんが何をしたかは）\n（絶対誰にも言わないでおこう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What Yu-chan did…）\n（I'll definitely keep it a secret from everyone…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4,
      "endTime": 51.526556877299996,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.333333300005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "監督",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-director001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、天動さん！　それにみなさんも\nこれから撮るシーンについて、ちょっといいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rui-san! And everyone else too.\nCan I talk to you about the upcoming scene for a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3,
      "endTime": 59.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、なんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ what is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9,
      "endTime": 61.6068027735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "監督",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-director002.m4a",
      "text": "カットしたキスシーンのところなんだけど\nやっぱり、演出的に盛り上げたいので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's about the cut kissing scene‚ but\nI'd like to add some excitement to it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9333312988,
      "endTime": 67.69333138459999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.2333312988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "チョコのような甘い口づけを、あなたへ\n――ハッピーバレンタイン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A sweet kiss like chocolate‚ to you.\n――Happy Valentine's.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.0333312988,
      "endTime": 76.1194536844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.4666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.4666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4666646321,
      "endTime": 77.79999796550001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.2999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "い～～や～～や～～！！\nこんなん、うちは絶対認めへんからなあ～～～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Noooo!!\nWe absolutely won't accept something like this!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2999979655,
      "endTime": 84.6425986517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8333312988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん落ち着いて～！\nいま本番中だってば～！　も～～～う！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan‚ calm down!\nWe're in the middle of the actual shoot! Come on!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8333312988,
      "endTime": 90.678002437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "邪魔せんといて、すみれちゃん！\nトリエルの……瑠依ちゃんの純潔のためなんやー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't get in the way‚ Sumire-chan!\nFor the purity of TRINITYAiLE and Rui-chan‚ we won't allow this!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8999979655,
      "endTime": 97.09352679119999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.0333312988
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.2999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "キスじゃなくってキス顔だけの撮影なんだから\n瑠依ちゃんの唇は無事だってば～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not a kiss‚ it's just a shot of a kissing face‚\nRui-chan's lips are safe!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2999979655,
      "endTime": 104.17065673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.3666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "キス顔が全国のお茶の間に流れるんなら同じことです！\n瑠依ちゃんの唇は、うちが、守るんや～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the kissing face is shown to the whole country‚ it's the same thing!\nRui-chan's lips‚ we will protect them~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3666646321,
      "endTime": 112.6403395273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.8333312988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "監督",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-director003.m4a",
      "text": "カーット！　いい感じだよ、天動さん\nもう一パターン撮っておこうか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cut! It looks good‚ Rui-san.\nShould we shoot one more take?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.8333312988,
      "endTime": 119.73333129880001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.9333312988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Please‚ go ahead!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9333312988,
      "endTime": 122.20852408409999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.5333312988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_05-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "一度ならず二度も、瑠依ちゃんの神聖なキス顔を……！\nゆ、許さん……その顔はうちだけのもんや～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not once but twice‚ the sacred kissing face of Rui-chan…!\nAh‚ I won't allow it… that face belongs to us only~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5333312988,
      "endTime": 134.1268749724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
